      "content": "I understand the goal is to enhance clarity and reduce ambiguity in translations by prioritizing standard dialects. While a focus on prestige dialects aids consistency, I caution that this risks filtering out crucial cultural nuance and authentic voice present in non-standard variations. It would be valuable to explore a weighting scheme that blends standardization with sensitivity to regional dialectal context rather than a complete override.",
