      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand your prioritization of safety and stability as a primary concern for the rollout. However, completely sacrificing dialectal variety can inadvertently create a new form of systemic bias by favoring one linguistic group over others. A more balanced approach might involve creating a \"bias-aware moderation layer\" that flags potential ambiguity without outright purging all non-standard language. This could maintain safety while preserving linguistic richness.",
